# shadcn/ui Component Patterns

## Sidebar System Usage

### Required Components

Always use these shadcn/ui Sidebar components from [src/components/ui/sidebar.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/sidebar.tsx):

- `SidebarProvider` - Wrap entire layout
- `Sidebar` - Main sidebar container with `collapsible="icon"`
- `SidebarContent` - Scrollable content area
- `SidebarHeader` - Top section for branding
- `SidebarFooter` - Bottom section for controls
- `SidebarGroup` - Navigation groups
- `SidebarMenu` - Menu container
- `SidebarMenuItem` - Individual menu items
- `SidebarMenuButton` - Interactive menu buttons
- `SidebarTrigger` - Toggle button
- `SidebarInset` - Main content area

### Layout Structure

```tsx
<SidebarProvider>
  <Sidebar collapsible="icon">
    <SidebarHeader />
    <SidebarContent>
      <SidebarGroup>
        <SidebarMenu>
          <SidebarMenuItem>
            <SidebarMenuButton />
          </SidebarMenuItem>
        </SidebarMenu>
      </SidebarGroup>
    </SidebarContent>
    <SidebarFooter />
  </Sidebar>
  <SidebarInset>
    <header />
    <main />
  </SidebarInset>
</SidebarProvider>
```

